      "id": "intro-0",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "一个用于构建 API 的现代、快速（高性能）的 web 框架，使用 Python 3.6+ 并基于标准的 Python 类型提示"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-1",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%20FastAPI",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "%24%20pip%20install%20%22fastapi%5Ball%5D%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-2",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "可以分开来安装",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "假如你想将应用程序部署到生产环境，你可能要执行以下操作："
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-3",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "$ pip install fastapi"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-4",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "并且安装 `uvicorn` 来作为服务器："
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-5",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "%24%20pip%20install%20%22uvicorn%5Bstandard%5D%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-6",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "运行代码",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "$ uvicorn main:app --reload"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-7",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "Python: `3.9.5` FastAPI: `0.103.1`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-8",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "最小程序",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "下面代码会直接启动http服务，也可以使用 `uvicorn main:app --reload`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-9",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "python",
      "code": "from fastapi import FastAPI\nimport uvicorn\n\napp = FastAPI()"
    },
